---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Shingai Thornton and Halcyonic Systems">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="ab-title">About</h1>

    <div class="ab-intro">
      <div class="ab-kingfisher">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="Halcyonic kingfisher" class="ab-bird" />
      </div>
      <div class="ab-story">
        <p>
          The halcyon is the kingfisher of Greek myth — the bird that nests on calm seas.
          Ancient sailors believed it could still the waves during its brooding days, creating
          a window of peace in the middle of winter storms. That stillness is what we pursue:
          a point of formal rigor in the chaos of transdisciplinary complexity.
          The stillness isn't about the work being calm. It's about what internalizing
          systems concepts does to the person holding the lens.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ab-bio">
      <p>
        I'm Shingai Thornton. I defended my M.S. thesis in Systems Science at Binghamton University
        in April 2026.
      </p>
      <p>
        Before that, I spent a decade researching blockchains, cryptoeconomics, and political economy.
        Halcyonic Systems is where this work comes together — formal systems science applied to
        governance, cryptoeconomics, and brain-inspired computing.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="ab-lineage">
      <h2 class="ab-section-header">Intellectual Lineage</h2>
      <p>
        Mobus convinced me systems science is a real discipline worth a life's work.
        Joslyn showed me that mathematics isn't notation &mdash; it's a language precise
        enough to say what systems actually are. Bertalanffy's philosophy reminds me why
        the field exists: we've reached diminishing returns on fragmentation and have
        barely scratched the surface of what integration and composition can reveal.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CommutingTriangle hidden 2026-04-28: Labs/Ventures vertices not yet operational.
         Resurface when all three layers have substance, or reframe as pure theoretical result
         (Klir→Bunge→Mobus convergence) without the org structure overlay.
         Component lives at src/components/CommutingTriangle.astro -->


    <div class="ab-connect">
      <h2 class="ab-section-header">Connect</h2>
      <div class="ab-links">
        <a href="mailto:shingai@halcyonic.systems" class="ab-link">
          shingai@halcyonic.systems <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/halcyonic-systems" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ab-link">
          GitHub <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://halcyonic.discourse.group" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ab-link">
          Forums <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://ideas.halcyonic.systems" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ab-link">
          Substack <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .ab-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-frost-slate);
  }

  .ab-intro {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .ab-kingfisher {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ab-bird {
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ab-story {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .ab-story p {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-frost-slate-dim);
  }

  .ab-bio {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .ab-bio p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-frost-slate-dim);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .ab-section-header {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-frost-teal-dim);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .ab-lineage, .ab-architecture {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-frost-border);
  }

  .ab-lineage p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-frost-slate-dim);
  }

  .ab-connect {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-frost-border);
  }

  .ab-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ab-link {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-frost-teal);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ab-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .ab-intro {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
